	<ThingDef ParentName="Heyra_SciFiArmorBase">
		<defName>Heyra_Snipersuit</defName>
		<label>Heyran sniper suit</label>
		<description>This bodysuit provides very limited protection, but the bionic fibers throughout the suit assist the wearer in shooting. The wearer is empowered to lift and hold a large-caliber gun without fatigue. In addition, the suit corrects the wearer's shooting posture, improves accuracy, and reduces recoil.</description>
